(96, 212, 'Girls Hostel', 'girls-hostel', '<center style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: medium; line-height: normal;">\r\n<h2 style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 22px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #000080;"><img src="images/girl_hostel4.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="365" /></h2>\r\n</center>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; color: #000080;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Infrastucture</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" align="justify">     Girls Hostel building is two storied .For girls, there is one hostel building having 14 rooms. The Hostel campus is designed for 36 students ,however it accommodates 55 girls students.Further it comprises ofhostel office ,rector quarter.</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; color: #000080;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Amenities</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" align="justify">     The girl students are provided with basic amenities like cot ,table ,chair ,cupboard in their rooms .The rooms are spacious, airy and illuminated. The surrounding is landscaped with greenery. Students common room has TV sets and carom .The water supply is for 24 hours with water purifier. A local news paper is available in common room.For girls.A generator ensures electric power supply to dinning hall and common rooms.The college gymkhana ground is near the hostel for playing outdoor games.First Aid Box is available in girls Hostel. The hostel campus maintenance like cleaning / sweeping , pest control is out sourced. The electrical repairs and security services are round the clock.</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; color: #000080;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Intake capacity</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" align="justify">     Total intake capacity of girls hostel is 36 girl students with addition of 19 students. Only one seat is reserved for national level sports candidate from all branches.Girls mess is run on co-operative basis by students committee.The monthly bill is calculated on actual expenses.</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; color: #000080;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Rules and Regulations</span></span></p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal;" align="justify">     Ragging is strictly prohibited. The Maharashtra Legislative Council has passed a bill (L C Bill Number ix of 1999) to prohibit ragging in educational institutions in the State of Maharashtra on 7th April 1999. As per this bill - Ragging within or outside of any educational institution is strictly prohibited. Whosoever directly or indirectly commits, participates in, abets or progagates ragging within or outside any educational institution shall on conviction, be punished, as per the rules. Any student convicted of an offence of ragging shall be dismissed from the educational institution and such student shall not be admitted to any other educational institution for a period of five years from the date of order of such dismissal.</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: normal; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; color: #000080;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Fee Structure (per year per student)</span></span><span style="color: #000000; font-family: Verda